<plot>A husband, reading a humorous newspaper article about how the town's female population is being overcome by a new "disease"--kimono-itis--thinks it's a real disease and rushes home to make sure his wife is OK. When he finds a note saying that she's gone to town to have her kimono cut, he frantically tries to get back to town to save her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?018175</url></doc>
